Package: libhtml-escape-perl
Source: libhtml-escape-perl (1.10-1)
Version: 1.10-1+b1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Debian Perl Group <pkg-perl-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 42
Depends: perl (>= 5.28.0-3), perlapi-5.28.0, libc6 (>= 2.14)
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/HTML-Escape
Description: provides extremely fast HTML escaping
 HTML::Escapes provides a function which escapes HTML's special characters. It
 performs a similar function to PHP's htmlspecialchars.
 .
 This module uses XS for better performance, but it also provides a pure perl
 version.
